spec_data.Name: python2-Pyped
spec_data.Description:
Pyped is a command-line tool that let you process another command
output with a Python one-liner like Perl or AWK.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:28:57 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Replace sed/grep/cut/awk by letting you execute Python one-liners
